    "asOf": "2025-02-05",
    "date": "2025-07-13T22:40:46Z",
    "text": "Stop Funding Our Adversaries Act of 2023\n\nThis bill prohibits federal agencies from conducting or supporting, either directly or indirectly, research that will be conducted by (1) China's government; (2) the Chinese Communist Party (CCP); (3) any agent\u00a0or instrumentality of China's government or the CCP; or (4) any entity owned or controlled by China or the CCP."
